# Optional — only needed if you want Google routing & Places autocomplete.
# Leave empty to use free OpenStreetMap backends (OSRM + Nominatim).
#
# If you do use Google, enable these APIs in your project:
#   - Routes API    (turn-by-turn directions)
#   - Geocoding API (address → lat/lng)
#   - Places API    (autocomplete in phone UI)
#
# Alternatively, paste the key directly in the app under Settings → Routing.
# Keys entered there are stored on the device and do not require a build.

VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_KEY=
